title: For Sale:  PTR 91
postcontent: The PTR 91 is a clone of the cold war era German G3. Of the clones this is the highest quality version. PTR also stands for "Poverty Tier Rifle" if you can blow your wad on a SCAR 17, but you still want a battle rifle this is the gun for you. Comes equipped with a bull barrel, standard flash hider, diopter rear sight, and pic rails for bi-pods and scopes. The savage piece of German engineering also comes with 10 surplus magazines all of which function well. If you haven't discovered the joy of roller delayed blow back you are in for a treat this thing will kick your ass and take your wife out for dinner afterwords. This thing will also fling your brass 20 yards down range so your work area will never be crowded with brass. This also comes with the sight adjustment tool, which makes it easier to adjust the sight than using needle nose pliers. There is a huge aftermarket for this thing so you can build it out to your hearts desire. Bambi doesn't stand a chance when you roll in with 200 rounds of Real Fuckin' NATO and detachable box mags. In person sales only bring your Carry permit and a drivers license and be prepared to sign a bill of sale or arrange for an ffl transfer and we can meet at your favorite NOVA gun shop. Make an offer and let's make a deal if you have cool stuff to trade I'll entertain it, but cash and crypto are king.
